 data-target=\"#feedbackModal_main_3615847\" data-toggle=\"modal\" role=\"button\" tabindex=\"0\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"ico-feedback\"><use xlink:href=\"#ico-feedback\"></use></svg><span class=\"zDocsFeedbackButtonText\"> Feedback</span></span></div></div><div class=\"zDocsTopicActionsMobile\"><button aria-label=\"Show topic actions\" data-toggle=\"dropdown\" id=\"zDocsTopicActionsMobile\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"ico-ellipsis-h\"><use xlink:href=\"#ico-ellipsis-h\"></use></svg></button><div class=\"dropdown-menu zDocsDropdownMenu zDocsTopicActionsMobileDropdown dropdown-menu-right\"></div></div><div style=\"flex-basis: 100%; height: 0px;\"></div><ul class=\"zDocsTopicPageDetails\"><li class=\"zDocsTopicPageDate css-cinqea\">Last Updated<span class=\"css-cinqea\">Okt 09, 2024</span></li><li class=\"zDocsAiTopicSummaryDetailsItem\"><button class=\"zDocsAiTopicSummaryButton\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"ico-topic-summary\"><use xlink:href=\"#ico-topic-summary\"></use></svg>Summarize</button></li><li class=\"spacer\" role=\"presentation\"></li><div class=\"zDocsLabelWrapper\"><ul><li class=\"zDocsLabel\"><a aria-describedby=\"hyperLinkFacetsTooltip\" class=\"css-ettsdk\" data-tooltip-content=\"Search all site by tag: Uniface\" data-tooltip-id=\"hyperLinkFacetsTooltip\" href=\"/de-DE/search?labelkey=prod_uniface\" stylesprops=\"[object Object]\"><svg aria-label=\"Tag\" class=\"ico-tag\" role=\"img\"><use xlink:href=\"#ico-tag\"></use></svg>Uniface</a></li><li class=\"zDocsLabel\"><a aria-describedby=\"hyperLinkFacetsTooltip\" class=\"css-ettsdk\" data-tooltip-content=\"Search all site by tag: 10.4\" data-tooltip-id=\"hyperLinkFacetsTooltip\" href=\"/de-DE/search?labelkey=uniface_10.4\" stylesprops=\"[object Object]\"><svg aria-label=\"Tag\" class=\"ico-tag\" role=\"img\"><use xlink:href=\"#ico-tag\"></use></svg>10.4</a></li></ul></div></ul></header><div class=\"zDocsTopicPageBody\" data-prismjs-copy=\"Copy\" data-prismjs-copy-error=\"Copy failed! Use Ctrl + C instead.\" data-prismjs-copy-success=\"Copied!\"><div class=\"zDocsTopicPageBodyContent wide\" dir=\"ltr\"><div id=\"zDocsAiSummaryContaineruniface_104sgs1665702580867.html\"></div><div><article class=\"hascomments\" data-page=\"bundle:uniface_104/enus/sgs1665702580867.html\" id=\"bundle:uniface_104/enus/sgs1665702580867.html\"><main role=\"main\"><article aria-labelledby=\"ariaid-title1\" class=\"dita\" id=\"sgs1665702580867\" role=\"article\">\n<h1 class=\"title topictitle1\" id=\"ariaid-title1\">\n      Secondary Window\n </h1>\n<div class=\"body refbody\"><p class=\"shortdesc\">A secondary window can be displayed or moved outside the bounds of the application shell. It is usually associated with a primary window, and is used to contain information that is dependent on an object in the primary window. It is defined by setting the window property <span class=\"ph uicontrol\">Window Type</span> to <code class=\"ph codeph\">Secondary</code>.\n </p>\n<section class=\"section\" id=\"sgs1665702580867__section_wgt_kcx_swb\"><h2 class=\"title sectiontitle\" id=\"d87181e57\">Description</h2>\n<p class=\"p\" id=\"sgs1665702580867__p_d100172e1_d100173e1_d100174e1\">A secondary window can have a title bar, but it cannot\n        be minimized or maximized, and it cannot have a system menu.</p>\n<p class=\"p\" id=\"sgs1665702580867__p_d100175e1_d100176e1_d100177e1\">You can set the <span class=\"ph uicontrol\">Modality &amp;\n          Attachment</span> properties for a secondary window.</p>\n<div class=\"note note note_note\" id=\"sgs1665702580867__note_lkw_lcx_swb\"><span class=\"note__title\">Note:</span> If you choose <span class=\"ph uicontrol\">Modal, Attached</span>,\n        other forms in the application cannot be accessed until the secondary window is\n        closed.</div>\n<p class=\"p\" id=\"sgs1665702580867__p_d100178e1_d100179e1_d100180e1\">Setting the <span class=\"ph uicontrol\">Window Type</span> to\n          <code class=\"ph codeph\">Secondary</code>also sets the following properties:</p>\n<div class=\"table-wrap\"><table class=\"table\" count-columns=\"2\" id=\"sgs1665702580867__table_d11684e1_d11685e1_d11686e1\"><caption></caption><colgroup><col/><col/></colgroup><thead class=\"thead\">\n<tr class=\"row\" dir=\"ltr\">\n<th class=\"entry\" dir=\"ltr\" id=\"sgs1665702580867__table_d11684e1_d11685e1_d11686e1__entry__1\"> Property </th>\n<th class=\"entry\" dir=\"ltr\" id=\"sgs1665702580867__table_d11684e1_d11685e1_d11686e1__entry__2\"> Value </th>\n</tr>\n</thead><tbody class=\"tbody\">\n<tr class=\"row\" dir=\"ltr\">\n<td class=\"entry\" dir=\"ltr\" headers=\"sgs1665702580867__table_d11684e1_d11685e1_d11686e1__entry__1\">\n<span class=\"ph uicontrol\">System Menu,</span>\n</td>\n<td class=\"entry\" dir=\"ltr\" headers=\"sgs1665702580867__table_d11684e1_d11685e1_d11686e1__entry__2\">\n<p class=\"p\">\n<code class=\"ph codeph\">False</code>\n</p>\n</td>\n</tr>\n<tr class=\"row\" dir=\"ltr\">\n<td class=\"entry\" dir=\"ltr\" headers=\"sgs1665702580867__table_d11684e1_d11685e1_d11686e1__entry__1\">\n<span class=\"ph uicontrol\">Iconize</span>\n</td>\n<td class=\"entry\" dir=\"ltr\" headers=\"sgs1665702580867__table_d11684e1_d11685e1_d11686e1__entry__2\">\n<p class=\"p\">\n<code class=\"ph codeph\">False</code>\n</p>\n</td>\n</tr>\n<tr class=\"row\" dir=\"ltr\">\n<td class=\"entry\" dir=\"ltr\" headers=\"sgs1665702580867__table_d11684e1_d11685e1_d11686e1__entry__1\">\n<span class=\"ph uicontrol\">Maximize</span>\n</td>\n<td class=\"entry\" dir=\"ltr\" headers=\"sgs1665702580867__table_d11684e1_d11685e1_d11686e1__entry__2\">\n<p class=\"p\">\n<code class=\"ph codeph\">False</code>\n</p>\n</td>\n</tr>\n</tbody></table></div>\n</section>\n</div>\n</article></main></article>\n</div></div></div><div class=\"bottomFeedback\"><div aria-labelledby=\"bottomFeedbackText\" class=\"bottomFeedbackContent\" role=\"group\"><span class=\"bottomFeedbackText\" id=\"bottomFeedbackText\">Was this topic helpful?</span><div class=\"bottomFeedbackButtonGroup\"><a data-backdrop=\"static\" data-target=\"#feedbackModal_bottom_3615847\" data-toggle=\"modal\" href=\"#\" role=\"button\" type=\"button\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"ico-thumbs-up\"><use xlink:href=\"#ico-thumbs-up\"></use></svg><span>Like</span></a><a data-backdrop=\"static\" data-target=\"#feedbackModal_bottom_3615847\" data-toggle=\"modal\" href=\"#\" role=\"button\" type=\"button\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"ico-thumbs-down\"><use xlink:href=\"#ico-thumbs-down\"></use></svg><span>Dislike</span></a></div></div></div><div style=\"position: fixed; bottom: 170px; right: 70px; cursor: pointer; transition-duration: 0.2s; transition-timing-function: linear; transition-delay: 0s; z-index: 3; opacity: 0; visibility: hidden; transition-property: opacity, visibility;\"><button aria-label=\"Scroll to top\" class=\"zDocsScrollTopBtn\" data-tooltip-content=\"Scroll to top\" data-tooltip-id=\"zDocsBackToTopToolTip\" id=\"zDocsScrollToTop\" type=\"button\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"ico-next\"><use xlink:href=\"#ico-next\"></use></svg></button></div></body></html>", "text": "Secondary Window Add to My Topics Add selected topic and subtopics Add Topic & Subtopics with topic head Add entire publication Watch Download PDF Save selected topic Save selected topic and subtopics Save entire publication Share Email Link Copy Link Feedback Last Updated Okt 09, 2024 Summarize Uniface 10.4 Secondary Window A secondary window can be displayed or moved outside the bounds of the application shell. It is usually associated with a primary window, and is used to contain information that is dependent on an object in the primary window. It is defined by setting the window property Window Type to Secondary . Description A secondary window can have a title bar, but it cannot be minimized or maximized, and it cannot have a system menu. You can set the Modality & Attachment properties for a secondary window. Note: If you choose Modal, Attached , other forms in the application cannot be accessed until the secondary window is closed. Setting the Window Type to Secondary also sets the following properties: Property Value System Menu, False Iconize False Maximize False Was this topic helpful? Like Dislike"}